<section class="Section">
	<div class="Container Container--centered">
		<h1><small>On Radio4000</small> everyone <small>has</small> one radio<small>, only one</small></h1>
		<p>
			In your unique radio you add music, any music you enjoy.<br>
			From this constraint you gain freedom. When you like a song, add it to your radio.
		</p>
		<p>
			Your personality gives soul to your radio.<br>
			All the music you listen to and their variety compose a harmonious whole.
			Their common denominator is the fact that you liked them, so don't worry about classifying.
		</p>
	</div>
</section>

